  "detailed_description": "<h1>Coming soon - Grunn!</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Botanik is a small relaxing game about a geometric-shaped gardener that takes care of various plants. <br><br><i>Note: a working internet connection is required to play this game.</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1135160/extras/1ddf589fe555e2ef371a4abaeea31f9b.poster.avif?t=1726498035\" width=600 height=370 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1135160/extras/1ddf589fe555e2ef371a4abaeea31f9b.webm?t=1726498035\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1135160/extras/1ddf589fe555e2ef371a4abaeea31f9b.mp4?t=1726498035\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> At least 10 minutes of playtime (and way more if you enjoy watering your plants).<br></li><li> Take care of your own plants.<br></li><li> Relax in your own glasshouse.<br></li><li> Visit the gardens of other players.<br></li><li> Cute characters and animations.<br></li><li> Unlock new seeds by taking good care of your plants.</li></ul><br><strong>Controls</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Left mouse button to move camera & interact.</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1135160/extras/c350ac25322f0cc81d29044611c576b9.avif?t=1726498035\" width=200 height=70 /></span><br>Sokpop makes a new game every two weeks!<br>Subscribe for 3$ per month at ",
